OL,6,FA statue of Jesus on a crucifix has
OL,7,Fbeen "stolen" using an 'electric saw'
OL,8,Ffrom outside a church.
OL,10,FA kneeling angel and kneeling figure
OL,11,Fof St Bernadette were also thought to
OL,12,Fhave been swiped from St Luke's in
OL,13,FIrlams o'th Height, .
OL,15,FA post shared by The Parish of Our
OL,16,FLady of Hope said it suspects the
OL,17,Fthree statues were taken with the use
OL,18,Fof an electric saw and that 'drag
OL,19,Fmarks' on the ground show the figures
OL,20,Fwere likely taken to a vehicle in the
OL,21,Fcar park.
