OL,6,FThe parish is urging any potential
OL,7,Fwitnesses to come forward and is
OL,8,Fasking local residents to check their
OL,9,Fdoorbell cameras to establish an exact
OL,10,Ftime the figures were stolen.
OL,12,FIt is currently thought they were
OL,13,Ftaken at some stage overnight between
OL,14,FJanuary 21 and 22.
OL,16,FParishioner Paul Ashton said: "The
OL,17,Fparishioners are shocked that such a
OL,18,Ftheft should happen to us.
