OL,3,CStatue of Jesus 'stolen' from church
OL,4,Cusing 'electric saw'
OL,6,F"The statue of Jesus on the crucifix
OL,7,Fwas originally in our old church and
OL,8,Fmeans so much to us.
OL,10,F"It is not just our parishioners, but
OL,11,Falso our neighbours, who find it
OL,12,Funbelievable that we should be
OL,13,Ftargeted in this way.
OL,15,F"We would ask anyone who is offered
OL,16,Fthese statues to get in touch with us
OL,17,Fand we are grateful for any
OL,18,Finformation that will help get these
OL,19,Fthree statues returned to us."
